text: Phira'aunale bhanna thalyoh ke timiharule maile anumati dinubhanda agadi nai musama visvasa garihalyau? Nihsandeha yo e'uta sadayantra thiyo jasako timile yasa nagarama karyanvayana garyau, taki tyasaka nivasiharula'i yahambata nikalna saka. Tasartha aba timila'i vastavikata thaha bha'ihalnecha
